department: Art of Africa and the Americas
description: Vase in shape of a human figure with two running, confronted warriors painted on breast.  The face is vigorously modeled, with painted designs on the cheekbones, but the arms and legs are done in very low relief.  The lower half of the vase has a rough, pebbled surface.  Spout which rises from head is chipping.
title: Vase in the form of a human figure
